Package: cnvr
Type: Package
Title: Visualize array signal and copy number calls
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Mahmoud Ahmed
Maintainer: Mahmoud Ahmed <mahmoud.ahmed@icr.ac.uk>
Description: Create heatmaps and scatter plots of copy number calls and array
    intensities. The package contain utility functions to read in the necessary
    files as well as obtaining and plotting gene models.
